Package: mpb2
Title: Mixed Poisson Beta Distribution
Version: 0.8
Author: Lisa Amrhein [aut], Kumar Harsha [aut, cre], Christiane Fuchs [aut]
Maintainer: Kumar Harsha <kumar.harsha@tum.de>
Authors@R: c(
  person("Lisa", "Amrhein", email="lisa.amrhein@helmholtz-muenchen.de", role="aut"),
  person("Kumar", "Harsha", email="kumar.harsha@tum.de", role=c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Christiane", "Fuchs", email="christiane.fuchs@helmholtz-muenchen.de", role="aut"))
Description: This package includes the density, distribution function, quantile function and random
  generation for the mixed poisson-beta distribution. Also included is a function for 
  Kummer's (confluent hypergeometric function of the 1st kind) function and a Gillespie algorithm
  implementation for the mixed-poisson-beta distribution.
